In a letter from his legal representation Gildenhuys Malatji, Finance Minister Pravin Gordhan has declined to meet with Brigadier Nyameka&nbsp;Xaba stating he has nothing further to say on the matter of the alleged SARS rogue unit.Read the letter from his lawyers&nbsp;here. This is the letter the Hawks initially sent to Gildenhuys Malatji.&nbsp;Gordhan has since responded with a statement which you can view here.&nbsp;